</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[527,621,1964,1990]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
, holotype, ♀ (CNC). 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[877,898,1964,1990]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">A</emphasis>
. Head, lateral view. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1143,1163,1964,1990]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">B</emphasis>
